value: Breeds in the high-arctic north Atlantic region, on Devon Island, Baffin Island, northeastern Greenland, Spitsbergen, Bear Island, Franz Joseph Land, and probably Novaya Zemlya. Migratory: outside the breeding season frequents mainly the low-arctic parts of the Atlantic Ocean, occasionally straggling into the northern parts of the boreal zone.
